## Overview

This file declares which focus groups are impacted by this concept and tracks approval status. Each impact becomes an approval requirement before implementation.

**Cross-Cutting Support:** A single concept can impact multiple focus groups. For example, "OAuth Integration" might declare impacts on Security (token validation), API (endpoint changes), and Frontend (login UI).

